propertyDefinitions.name: UseDate
propertyDefinitions.displayDescription: Filename should include the current date. See Filename Date Format for the formatting.

propertyDefinitions.name: InboxFilenameFilter
propertyDefinitions.displayDescription: Simple Regular Expression to filter filenames to process in the inbox.  E.g. ^([^_]+)_([^_]+)_([^_]+)_([^_]+)_([^.]+)(\.txt|\.xls)$

propertyDefinitions.name: OutboxFilenameFilter
propertyDefinitions.displayDescription: Simple Regular Expression to filter filenames to process in the outbox.  E.g. ^([^_]+)_([^_]+)_([^_]+)_([^_]+)_([^.]+)(\.txt|\.xls)$

propertyDefinitions.name: InProcessExtension
propertyDefinitions.displayDescription: The filename extension used when a file is currently being processed. When E2net begins processing a message file, the filename extension is changed to this value. The default is .prc

propertyDefinitions.name: TransportRetryLimit
propertyDefinitions.displayDescription: The number of times to retry due to not receiving a HTTP 200 response from trading partner web server.
